<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="it-is-said-that">it is said that ...</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>据说…：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is said that about 30,000 people attended this first exhibition. 
据说约有3万人参加了这次首展。</p><footer>译林⑧ – 1</footer></div>

<p>注: it is said that ... 常可与be said to ... 互换。  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is said that he is an artist. / He is said to be an artist.
据说他是个艺术家。</p></div></div>